<div></div>
<div><strong>Take a 2nd look when you buy your sunnies...</strong></div>
</div>
<div class="field-item">
<div class="field-item-image"><a class="imagefield imagefield-lightbox2 imagefield-lightbox2-Gallery imagefield-field_galleryimages imagecache imagecache-field_galleryimages imagecache-Gallery imagecache-field_galleryimages-Gallery lightbox-processed" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #90416a; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.sosensational.co.uk/sites/default/files/iStock_000013835608XSmall%20(425x282)%20(2)_0.jpg" rel="lightbox[field_galleryimages][If you have an angular face and wear your sunnies on your head, we have a fabulous style tip for you. Of course you know that the frames need to suit you. But, in addition, the shape that the pair of glasses form when they sit on your head, head-band style, needs to work with your face-shape, too. So, if you have an angular face, the glasses should not be the curvy, wraparound kind, but should form a right-angle at the sides.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.sosensational.co.uk/sites/default/files/iStock_000013835608XSmall (425x282) (2)_0.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; id=&quot;lightbox2-download-link-text&quot;&gt;Download Original&lt;/a&gt;]"><img class=" alignleft" title=" Take a 2nd look when you buy your sunnies..." src="http://www.sosensational.co.uk/sites/default/files/imagecache/Gallery/iStock_000013835608XSmall%2520%2528425x282%2529%2520%25282%2529_0.jpg" alt=" Take a 2nd look when you buy your sunnies..." width="145" height="145" /></a></div>
<div class="field-item-other">
<div class="field-item-other-title">If you have an angular face and wear your sunnies on your head, we have a fabulous style tip for you. Of course you know that the frames need to suit you. But, in addition, the shape that the pair of glasses form when they sit on your head, head-band style, needs to work with your face-shape, too. So, if you have an angular face, the glasses should not be the curvy, wraparound kind, but should form a right-angle at the sides.</div>
