<div>[su_divider top="no" size="1"]</div>
<div></div>
<div><strong>Sleeve advice, part 2: Get the right sleeve length</strong></div>
</div>
<div class="field-item">
<div class="field-item-image"><a class="imagefield imagefield-lightbox2 imagefield-lightbox2-Gallery imagefield-field_galleryimages imagecache imagecache-field_galleryimages imagecache-Gallery imagecache-field_galleryimages-Gallery lightbox-processed" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #90416a; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.sosensational.co.uk/sites/default/files/Acne,%20%C2%A390.jpg" rel="lightbox[field_galleryimages][When wearing short sleeves, ensure that the hem of the sleeve is (a) not in line with the crown of your bustline (as this will look like one continuous and widening line across the body - not a good look) and (b) does not end at the widest part of your arm, as this would make your arms look wider. And who needs that? &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.sosensational.co.uk/sites/default/files/Acne, Â£90.jpg&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; id=&quot;lightbox2-download-link-text&quot;&gt;Download Original&lt;/a&gt;]"><img class=" alignleft" title="Sleeve advice, part 2: Get the right sleeve length " src="http://www.sosensational.co.uk/sites/default/files/imagecache/Gallery/Acne%252C%2520%25C2%25A390.jpg" alt="How to choose the right length short sleeve" width="108" height="145" /></a></div>
<div class="field-item-other">
<div class="field-item-other-title">When wearing short sleeves, ensure that the hem of the sleeve is (a) not in line with the crown of your bustline (as this will look like one continuous and widening line across the body - not a good look) and (b) does not end at the widest part of your arm, as this would make your arms look wider. And who needs that?</div>
</div>
